Thread 2
---------

Race condition
-------------
if multiple thread is trying is to access same object at the same time race condition occurs.
race condition always leads to inconsistent data.

how to avoid race condition
1. thread synchronization
--------------------------------
it is the process of executing threads in the sequential order where one thread will execute only after the other thread finish execution

2 ways:-
	1. synchronized methods
		are the methods which use synchronized keyword on methods.
	2. synchronized blocks
	
	